buttons

button: mineOre
name: Hand mine ore
desc: Mine a chunk of basic ore by hand.
icon: rock
cost: 0 credits
gives: 1 ore

button: refineMetal
name: Smelt metal
desc: Turn ore into usable metal.
icon: bar
cost: 5 ore
gives: 1 metal

button: growCrystal
name: Grow crystals
desc: Use metal and energy to grow rare crystals.
icon: gem
cost: 5 metal, 10 energy
gives: 1 crystal

button: runExperiment
name: Run experiment
desc: Spend crystal and energy to gain research.
icon: flask
cost: 2 crystal, 25 energy
gives: 1 research

buildings

building: workshop
name: Workshop
desc: Produces credits by making simple goods from metal.
icon: factory
cost: 50 credits, 10 metal
gives: 1 credits

building: powerPlant
name: Power plant
desc: Generates energy from credits and ore.
icon: lightning
cost: 100 credits, 20 ore
gives: 2 energy

building: mine
name: Automated mine
desc: Continuously generates ore.
icon: rock
cost: 150 credits
gives: 3 ore

building: smelter
name: Smelter
desc: Automatically converts ore into metal.
icon: bar
cost: 250 credits, 30 ore
gives: 2 metal

building: crystalLab
name: Crystal lab
desc: Grows rare crystals using metal and energy.
icon: gem
cost: 500 credits, 50 metal, 50 energy
gives: 1 crystal

building: researchLab
name: Research lab
desc: Generates research over time.
icon: flask
cost: 800 credits, 5 crystal
gives: 1 research

building: spacePort
name: Spaceport
desc: Sells goods off‑world for lots of credits.
icon: rocket
cost: 1200 credits, 40 metal
gives: 10 credits

building: megaFactory
name: Mega factory
desc: A huge complex that boosts all production.
icon: factory
cost: 5000 credits, 50 metal, 10 crystal
gives: 25 credits

